README for mpv


OVERLAY NOTES

This board has no GPU acceleration at all (no Vulkan, glx disabled in Xorg — see xorg-server notes),
so vulkan/d3d11/gl/egl/gbm/drm/vaapi/vdpau/ wayland/cuda are all disabled here.
x11 and xv stay enabled — those are the actual outputs.
Use `mpv --vo=x11` or `--vo=xv`; any GPU-based vo will never work on this hardware.
 
mpv depends on libplacebo, but the upstream version can't be used as-is on this board — see the
libplacebo overlay and its own README for why and what was done there.
